history.content:
Hi all, 


The department will be hosting 25+ events on CalDay (Saturday, April 21st). I am looking for two volunteers who would be available to take pictures on that day. 

Events will be happening 9am-3pm. You might be available for a half-day, or just a couple of hours. Preferably, you have your own camera. If not, smart phone pictures should be sufficient. 

Please send me an email (nicolemcintyre@eecs.berkeley.edu) or respond if you're interested. Lunch provided. 


Thanks!
history.subject: Seeking Photographer for CalDay
